      • displayPoly

        public static SimplePolygon displayPoly(java.awt.Rectangle box,
                                        java.awt.Component comp,
                                        SimplePolygon poly)
        Calculate the display polygon in a component containers space from a true cropbox associated with a display component.
        Parameters:
        box - box in components image space
        comp - Component box is to be drawn for
        poly - polygon that may be written over to save allocating a new polygon. If null a new SimplePolygon will be constructed.
        Returns:
        polygon representing the box in the components containers space
